Tiny House Nation - Season 3, Episode 12




340 Sq. Ft. Pioneer House

The Grahams are gearing up to make a major move across the country and begin their next adventure as a family. They're looking for a craftsman style tiny house that's going to hold up against the brutal winters they will soon face and that packs enough functionality for the whole family.




Original Air Date: 29-Aug-2015
